</p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/2X/1/1e25b067bb223c558baf7655febb7b54134d99ad.png" data-download-href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/1e25b067bb223c558baf7655febb7b54134d99ad" title="1"><img src="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/1e25b067bb223c558baf7655febb7b54134d99ad_2_690x359.png" alt="1" data-base62-sha1="4iH4v4QvIh6qgXNirFBaCPUPhql" width="690" height="359" srcset="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/1e25b067bb223c558baf7655febb7b54134d99ad_2_690x359.png, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/1e25b067bb223c558baf7655febb7b54134d99ad_2_1035x538.png 1.5x, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/1e25b067bb223c558baf7655febb7b54134d99ad_2_1380x718.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/1e25b067bb223c558baf7655febb7b54134d99ad_2_10x10.png"></a></div><p></p>
<p>And when I type <a href="http://localhost:3000/wp/wp-json/wp/v2/cookielawinfo" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">http://localhost:3000/wp/wp-json/wp/v2/cookielawinfo</a> (where Frontity theme is), I get:<br>
</p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/2X/5/577d04d5304ecae4568f9d9768014e079a00cf3f.jpeg" data-download-href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/577d04d5304ecae4568f9d9768014e079a00cf3f" title="3"><img src="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/5/577d04d5304ecae4568f9d9768014e079a00cf3f_2_690x356.jpeg" alt="3" data-base62-sha1="ctXohsKgl34B7tLyRD1SVJ7LoGr" width="690" height="356" srcset="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/5/577d04d5304ecae4568f9d9768014e079a00cf3f_2_690x356.jpeg, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/5/577d04d5304ecae4568f9d9768014e079a00cf3f_2_1035x534.jpeg 1.5x, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/5/577d04d5304ecae4568f9d9768014e079a00cf3f_2_1380x712.jpeg 2x" data-small-upload="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/5/577d04d5304ecae4568f9d9768014e079a00cf3f_2_10x10.png"></a></div><p></p>
<p>I still don’t get what you mean with “posts” in this cookielawinfo CPT, though. Do you mean if I have added any custom posts except the ones that are already included in this GDPR Cookie Consent plugin (like shown in the picture below?).<br>
</p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/2X/2/202f99ef851e2fba3a03ca63d6622b4aa55a4887.png" data-download-href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/202f99ef851e2fba3a03ca63d6622b4aa55a4887" title="2"><img src="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/202f99ef851e2fba3a03ca63d6622b4aa55a4887_2_690x325.png" alt="2" data-base62-sha1="4AJgokeueEvM5ov2OMtpVtk3ekL" width="690" height="325" srcset="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/202f99ef851e2fba3a03ca63d6622b4aa55a4887_2_690x325.png, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/202f99ef851e2fba3a03ca63d6622b4aa55a4887_2_1035x487.png 1.5x, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/202f99ef851e2fba3a03ca63d6622b4aa55a4887_2_1380x650.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/202f99ef851e2fba3a03ca63d6622b4aa55a4887_2_10x10.png"></a></div><p></p>
<p>If that’s what you mean, as you can see in the picture, the answer is: no, I don’t.</p>
          <p><a href="https://community.frontity.org/t/gdpr-suggestion/1452/33">Read full topic</a></p>
