        <dc:creator><![CDATA[mburridge]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Do you have the GDPR Cookie Consent plugin installed in WordPress? That plugin provides the <code>cookielawinfo</code> CPT. However it doesn’t add the CPT to the REST API, which is what the code snippet you included above does - it adds the <code>cookielawinfo</code> CPT to the WordPress REST API.</p>
