      </item>
      <item>
        <title>GDPR Suggestion</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[mburridge]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Hi <a class="mention" href="https://community.frontity.org/u/tix">@tix</a></p>
<p>The <code>v2</code> is part of the WP REST API endpoint. It should be there.</p>
<p>When you don’t have it you get the message that no matching route was found - which is correct.</p>
<p>When you do have it you get an empty array. This indicates that the route was found, but there is no data so it’s returning an empty array. Ensure that the <code>cookielawinfo</code> CPT has some content in the WordPress admin pages.</p>
          <p><a href="https://community.frontity.org/t/gdpr-suggestion/1452/22">Read full topic</a></p>
        ]]></description>
        <link>https://community.frontity.org/t/gdpr-suggestion/1452/22</link>
        <pubDate>Wed, 13 Jan 2021 09:35:36 +0000</pubDate>
        <guid isPermaLink="false">community.frontity.org-post-1452-22</guid>
        <source url="https://community.frontity.org/t/gdpr-suggestion/1452.rss">GDPR Suggestion</source>
      </item>
